.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-REMOTE-BALANCE-MAX" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-remote-balance-max \- FEAT-2257 channel with highest remote_msat
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-remote-balance-max
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns the channel with the highest remote_msat balance (FEAT-2257).
.PP
Output: JSON with channel object containing peer_id, short_channel_id, remote_msat.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
